name: CliKintoneTest-82 Should return the error message when exporting the record with a draft API Token.
fullName: features/export.feature#CliKintoneTest-82 Should return the error message when exporting the record with a draft API Token.

steps.name: Given Load app ID of the app "app_for_draft_token" as env var: "APP_ID"
And Load app token of the app "app_for_draft_token" with exact permissions "view" as env var: "DRAFT_API_TOKEN"
When I run the command with args "record export --base-url $$TEST_KINTONE_BASE_URL --app $APP_ID --api-token $DRAFT_API_TOKEN"
Then I should get the exit code is non-zero
And The output error message should match with the pattern: "\[400] \[GAIA_IA02] The specified API token does not match the API token generated via an app."

labels.name: suite
labels.value: CliKintoneTest-82 Should return the error message when exporting the record with a draft API Token.
